  <brief_title>Predictive Value of Procalcitonin, CRP, Drain Fluid Culture, Il-6 and Tnf-α in Anastomotic Leakage</brief_title>
  <official_title>Predicting Value of Serum Procalcitonin, C-reactive Protein, and Drain Fluid Culture, Fluid Il-6 and Tnf-α Levels in Anastomotic Leakage Following Rectal Resection</official_title>
  <sponsors>
